      <section>
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Curious mind, passionate teacher. I’ve been teaching design and research methodology to undergrads for over 6 years. I focus on helping students connect theory to the real world through storytelling, sketching, and playful experimentation. My work sits at the intersection of design thinking, education, and everyday life.</p>
      </section>

